title: 09/10/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 09/10/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to Rich Eisen about last night's game. Has his thoughts on either team changed given their performances? HOF Manager Joe Torre calls in and shares stories from when President Bush threw out the 1st pitch after 9/11. And Kurt Warner explains his outlook for each of the rookie QBs.
